            "explain": "$\\frac{1}{1-0.9}=10$, and $\\log\\frac{1}{0.01\\cdot 0.25}=\\log 400\\approx 5.99$, so $t_{\\mathrm{mix}}\\le 10\\cdot 5.99\\approx 60$."
