            "answer": 15,
            "tol": 0,
            "explain": "$\\partial\\Delta^3$ has all subsets of $\\{1,2,3,4\\}$ except $\\{1,2,3,4\\}$ itself. That's $2^4 - 1 = 15$ faces. (4 vertices + 6 edges + 4 triangles + 1 empty = 15.)"
