            "answer": 0,
            "tol": 0.000001,
            "hint": "Substitute the parametrization and simplify to the defining equation.",
            "explain": "At $t=2$: $x=4-1=3$, $y=2(4-1)=6$. Then $y^2-x^3-x^2=36-27-9=0$, confirming the point $(3,6)$ lies on the cubic."
